{"tid":702785,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世界盃揭幕日 俄羅斯球迷遇同情戀情侶即場打鑊甘","createTime":"2018-06-15T07:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T09:42:01.000Z","uid":55981,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"082f5d2d81a582535191b0e0a11c710e2cbf4226","tid":702785,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529035079_f8a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529035079_f8a0.jpg&h=d79a9a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界盃東道主俄羅斯被稱為「戰鬥民族」，亦一直被視為場外的搞事份子，據外國傳媒報道，俄羅斯球迷在世界盃揭幕日即惹事生非，有英國球迷遭搶劫，更有法國的同性戀情侶被襲，需送醫接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n據《太陽報》報道，有一位英國球迷在莫斯科遭五個俄羅斯人襲擊，及後更被迫到提款機提取現金。不過，有消息指該位英國球迷遇劫時處於醉酒狀態，因此案發後未能向執法人員提供個人資訊，亦未知被搶走多少金錢。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據《PinkNews》網站報道，有一對法國同情戀情侶在聖彼德堡遇襲受重創，需送院接受治療，其中一位名為O Davrius的男子，在意外中被重擊腦部，顎骨同樣被打至骨裂。而兩位俄羅斯籍疑兇、25歲的Ismet Gaidarov及24歲的Rasul Magomedov則被拘捕。值得一提的是，俄羅斯對同性戀者的態度並不友好，巴西政府更曾呼籲訪俄的同志情侶勿於當地「放閃」，以保障人身安全。"},{"pid":"4e5bab80efa14aa00d8a3e7fe6ee139900712de6","tid":702785,"uid":55981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"同性戀先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b9dbf56669f66c7dc50657b5b767da92a5a3de","tid":702785,"uid":3454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"連登囝:打得好"},{"pid":"fef5889a17f69774588ea6ed2f56fc54fdb554f8","tid":702785,"uid":155818,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"7232a404c9386f468acd5889ef5e703c1270c8d5","tid":702785,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"World Cup RED ALERT: Stalinist Russian hooligans plot to attack fans over World War 2<br />\n<br />\nWORLD Cup 2018 football fans have been told to stay alert after claims Russian hooligans could attack Polish supporters over unsolved Soviet World War Two grievances.<br />\n<br />\nPoland fans at the Fifa tournament, which starts today, have been urged to watch out for aggressive behaviour from ultra-patriotic Russian football hooligans.<br />\n<br />\nThe warning comes ahead of the official World Cup 2018 Opening Ceremony today at 3:30pm UK time at Moscow's Luzhniki Stadium.<br />\n<br />\nOnline calls for violence have been revealed after Russians took offence to Poland removing Soviet-era memorials dedicated to fallen Red Army soldiers in the wake of World War Two.<br />\n<br />\n有消息指波蘭球迷將會所到攻擊"},{"pid":"a53e8ca965e9a4f59a0ce8107298600824dcbf7d","tid":702785,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"抵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8e8084e6fa539eb23631d5380e5a2715074069","tid":702785,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"我地戰鬥民族係真男人，有咩打左先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/russia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f755dc7908e55371322e5f5a288a7d2771bb43b9","tid":702785,"uid":46013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"打得好！同我大大力咁打!"},{"pid":"1472213c77a22080cbb73d0149d2499dce8639dd","tid":702785,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a60e188c5f221826c674e2815b21bcb86291c48","tid":702785,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b9dbf56669f66c7dc50657b5b767da92a5a3de","tid":702785,"uid":3454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"連登囝:打得好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"打得好"},{"pid":"4cbb4322427f87274719feadd1ca51bed9b36150","tid":702785,"uid":16595,"li